HEADWORD: Antichrist
<hw>An"ti*christ</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Antichristus</ets>, Gr. <?/; <grk>'anti`</grk> against +
<?/.]</ety> <def>A denier or opponent of Christ. Specif.: A great
antagonist, person or power, expected to precede Christ's second
coming.</def>⟦br⟧
